Hello everyone!
My name is Devin and I am a senior at Rutgers - Newark, NJ. I am a Video Production major and I am directing my very first short film.

I am asking for donations to purchase equipment, rent space, and to pay my actors. I am hiring professional actors and I am using professional equipment. I want this to be perfect and I want to showcase my talent and deliver an incredible story.

I am not going to lie, the last year has been extremely difficult for me. I am a full-time student and I haven't had a consistent job. I teach Zumba classes, Dance classes, and post on social media. Most of you know me as Yungdaddycack on TikTok or Instagram and have watched me dance all over your feed. I love the arts and I am passionate about what I do. I love to make people happy, to feel, to escape their reality. This is why my short film is so important to me and could launch my career as a filmmaker.

If you made it this far, I want to thank you for hearing me out. For those who donate, I appreciate you and thank you for your kindness and support. It will not go unnoticed! - Devin Santiago (Yungdaddycack) ❤️
